@model IEnumerable<AWWW_lab2_gr1.Models.Position>;
<h1>Pozycje</h1>
<p><a asp-action="AddOrUpdate">Dodaj pozycjÄ™</a> </p>
<table class="table">
    <thead>
        <tr>
            <th>ID</th>
            <th>Kategoria</th>
            <th>Opcje</th>
        </tr>
    </thead>
    <tbody>
        @foreach (var position in @Model)
        {
            <tr>
                <td>@position.Id</td>
                <td>@position.Name</td>
                <td>
                    <a asp-action="AddOrUpdate" asp-route-id="@position.Id">Edit</a>
                    <a asp-action="Details" asp-route-id="@position.Id">Details</a>
                    <a asp-action="Delete" asp-route-id="@position.Id">Delete</a>
                </td>
            </tr>
        }
    </tbody>

</table>
